                <p class="text-[11px] text-neutral-400">Shipping fees and localized taxation weights calculated during checkout flow sequence paths.</p>
                <button onclick="app.checkout.initiateCheckout()" class="w-full py-4 bg-neutral-900 text-white font-semibold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors rounded-none">Proceed to Checkout</button>
